《财经》杂志官方微信。
An official letter from Caijing magazine.
《财经》杂志由中国证券市场研究中心主办，1998年创刊，秉承“独立、独家、独到”的新闻理念，以权威性、公正性、专业性报道见长，是政经学界决策者、研究者、管理者的必读刊物。
"Caijing" magazine, sponsored by the China Securities Market Research Center, was founded in 1998, upholding the news concept of "independence, exclusivity and originality," and providing authoritative, impartial and professional reports.
。
.
中国现有确诊病例已降至1万以下。
The number of confirmed cases in China has dropped below 10,000.
国内已采取最严密的入境防疫检测措施。
The country has adopted the most stringent anti-epidemic measures.
美国继续在快车道上狂奔，但基本防疫措施已经得到重视和加强文丨《财经》数据研究员 徐进 图丨《财经》视觉中心 编辑丨郝洲一、境外输入病例北京居首，实施最严入境检疫措施图1今日国内简述：国内3月15日报告累计确诊病例80860例，武汉新增4例，湖北非武汉地区连续11日零新增。
The United States continues its drive on the fast track, but basic preventive measures have been emphasized and strengthened. Beijing leads the list of imported cases into Beijing, where 80 860 cases are reported on March 15, adding 4 cases to Wuhan and 11 consecutive days to non-Wuhan, Hubei province.
国内非湖北地区无本地新增。
There are no local additions in non-Hubei areas.
新增报告境外输入确诊病例12例（北京4例，广东4例，上海2例，云南1例，甘肃1例）。
A total of 12 confirmed cases were reported from abroad (4 in Beijing, 4 in Guangdong, 2 in Shanghai, 1 in Yunnan and 1 in Gansu).
即日起，北京实行最严密的入境检疫。
From now on, Beijing will carry out the most stringent quarantine measures.
对所有境外进京人员，包括从其他口岸进京的，进行14天的集中医学观察，费用自理。
All overseas visitors to Beijing, including those who enter Beijing from other ports, will receive intensive medical observation for 14 days at their own expense.
对有症状、有病史、有线索、有必要的必查，进行核酸检测。
To have symptom, have medical history, have clue, necessary necessary check, carry out nucleic acid test.
二、海外累计确诊病例首超国内，单日增幅进一步扩大图2海外累计确诊病例和累计死亡病例双双超过国内，新增数字毫无减退之意。
The cumulative number of confirmed cases overseas exceeds that in China, and the one-day increase further increases. Figure 2 The cumulative number of confirmed cases and cumulative deaths overseas both exceeds that of China.
与此同时，疫情在亚非多国蔓延，撒哈拉以南非洲已有23个国家报告新冠肺炎确诊病例。
Meanwhile, the epidemic is spreading across Asia and Africa, with 23 countries in sub-Saharan Africa reporting confirmed cases of new crown pneumonia.
图3欧盟新增病例增长继续呈加速态势，何时见顶尚未可知。
Figure 3. Growth in new cases in the EU continues to accelerate, with a peak yet to be seen.
韩国已经连续两日保持新增在两位数，疫情得到控制的判断进一步坐实。
South Korea has been adding double digits for two days in a row, further substantiating its claim that the outbreak is under control.
三、美国联邦政府加紧磋商防控措施图4美国的新增确诊已经朝着1000的级别大踏步迈进，继续行驶在快车道上。
FIGURE 4 The new diagnosis in the United States has taken a big step toward the 1, 000 mark as it continues on the fast track.
目前，美国仅剩西弗吉尼亚州未报告感染病例。
There are currently only no reported cases of infection in West Virginia.
该州面积较小、号称“山脉之州”，多为乡村地带，“没有很多国际旅行人士”。
The small state, known as "Mountain State," is mostly rural, and "has not many international travelers."
但州长吉姆·贾斯特斯表示，“病毒肯定已经在这里了，只是我们还没有发现。
But Governor Jim Jastus said: "The virus must be here, but we haven't found it yet.
”负责全国抗疫工作的美国副总统彭斯说，联邦政府正与各州政府商讨抗议措施细节，将于今日稍晚公布。
Vice President Burns, who oversees the nation's response to the epidemic, says the federal government is working with state governments to discuss details of the protests, which will be announced later today.
新一轮抗疫措施可能包括颁布实施宵禁、关闭餐厅等指引。
A new wave of anti-epidemic measures could include curfews and restaurant closures.
从3月16日早上开始，进入（白宫）区域的所有人，包括访客、记者团成员等，将被要求测量体温。
Starting on the morning of March 16, anyone entering the area, including visitors, members of the press corps, etc., will be asked to take their temperature.
美国疾控中心3月15日呼吁在未来8周内取消50人或50人以上的现场集体活动，以防止新冠病毒的传播。
CDC on March 15 called for 50 people or more to be eliminated in the next eight weeks to prevent the spread of the new cap virus.
该指导意见并不适用于学校、大学或企业等大型组织。
The guidance does not apply to large organizations such as schools, universities or businesses.
不过，纽约市在3月15日宣布，暂时关闭全市逾1,800家公立学校至4月20日，将有110万名学童、7.5万名教师受影响。
However, the city of New York announced on March 15 that it would temporarily close more than 1,800 public schools across the city, affecting 1.1 million schoolchildren and 75,000 teachers by April 20.
图4.1美国至今牢牢站在传染数为3.8的拟合线上。
Figure 4.1 The United States remains firmly on the fit line of 3.8.
以此数据趋势推算，美国虽疫情起步较晚但总病例数将明显超过湖北和意大利，略好于西欧5国（德国/法国/西班牙/瑞士/尼德兰）合计。
Extrapolating from this trend, the total number of cases in the United States will be significantly higher than that in Hubei and Italy and slightly better than that of the five Western European countries (Germany / France / Spain / Switzerland / Nederland) combined.
四、德国关闭部分边境，意大利新增死亡创新高图5西班牙已成为欧洲疫情第二严重的国家，仅次于意大利。
4. Germany closes some of its borders, Italy's new death toll rises 5 Spain has become Europe's second most affected country after Italy.
法国多地的口罩、免洗洗手液等防疫物资已脱销。
Many parts of France, such as surgical masks, sanitizers and other immunization supplies have been sold out.
德国政府决定，自3月16日早8时起关闭与法国、瑞士和奥地利的边境，但因工作原因往返边境的人员及货运不受影响。
The German Government has decided to close its borders with France, Switzerland and Austria as of 8 a.m. on 16 March, but the movement of persons and goods to and from the border for work reasons will not be affected.
这一措施，将由联邦警察执行，各州警察予以配合。
This measure will be implemented by the federal police, with the cooperation of the state police.
与此同时，德国铁路也将从下周起进一步减少境内车次，且鉴于当前出行乘客数大幅下降，列车上将不再进行查票。
German railways, meanwhile, will further reduce the number of domestic trains from next week and, given the current sharp drop in the number of passengers, will no longer be checked.
爱尔兰关闭酒吧两周。
Ireland closes bars for two weeks.
荷兰关闭学校、酒吧、餐厅至少两周。
Schools, bars and restaurants are closed in the Netherlands for at least two weeks.
图5.1我们发现假设传染数为3.9时（绿线）比3.8时（蓝线）能更好拟合西欧除意大利外5个主要疫情国的合计数据。
Figure 5.1 We found that the aggregate data for the five major endemic countries in Western Europe, excluding Italy, were better fitted at 3.9 (Green Line) than 3.8 (Blue Line).
说明其疫情严重程度超过意大利。
This means the epidemic is more severe than in Italy.
以现在的数据趋势，这5国的病例总数将远远超过湖北和意大利。
With current data trends, the total number of cases in these five countries will far exceed that in Hubei and Italy.
图6意大利一天之内新增死亡368人，创下新高，这已远超中国最高峰时单日新增死亡病例（254人）。
Figure 6 Italy's new death toll of 368 in a day is a record, far surpassing China's peak of 254 new deaths a day.
图6.1与想象不同的是，我们发现假设传染数为3.7比3.8时能够更好拟合意大利的数据。
Figure 6.1 Contrary to what is assumed, we found that the data for Italy are better fitted when the assumed infection rate is 3.7 to 3.8.
就当前数据趋势看，其未来总病例数将与湖北相当，并明显小于美国。
Current data trends indicate that the total number of future cases will be comparable to Hubei, and significantly smaller than that of the United States.
意大利似乎从3月10日（n37）以后向有偏离参照线，尚不能确认属于防控效果。
Italy appears to have deviated from the reference line since March 10 (n 37) and cannot yet be identified as a control effect.
明天将尝试分段拟合。
The subsection fitting will be attempted tomorrow.
五、韩国要打防疫持久战，京畿道再爆集体性感染事件图7韩国卫生部门3月16日强调，要做好准备打防疫持久战。
South Korea to fight a protracted epidemic, Gyeonggi Province re-explosion collective infection Figure 7 South Korean health authorities on March 16 to prepare for a protracted battle against epidemic diseases.
韩国中央防疫对策本部部长郑银敬称，综合专家、国际社会意见，新冠病毒恐怕难以在短期内消灭。
Zheng Yin-kwong, minister of the Central Anti-epidemic Policy of the Republic of Korea, said that comprehensive experts and the international community.
随着欧洲疫情进一步加重，韩国政府从3月16日起将特别入境检疫程序的适用范围扩大至欧洲全境。
The South Korean government extended the application of the special entry quarantine procedure to all parts of Europe from March 16 as the European epidemic deepened.
政府有关部门还正在考虑将该措施适用于所有国家和地区。
The relevant government departments are also considering extending this measure to all countries and regions.
京畿道城南市3月16日表示，城南市教会一天40人确诊新冠肺炎。
Gyeonggi Province, South City on March 16, the church in the city of 40 people a day confirmed the new crown pneumonia.
因此，与该教会有关的新冠肺炎确诊者增至46名。
As a result, the number of persons diagnosed with Newly Coronary Pneumonia associated with the Church increased to 46.
此前，该教会的牧师夫妻和教徒等6人，于3月9~15日依次确诊。
Prior to this, the Church of the pastor, husband and wife and religious six people, March 9-15, in order to confirm the diagnosis.
据调查，该教会的确诊者们在3月8日一起进行过礼拜。
According to the investigation, the church's confirmed people together on March 8 to worship.
随着出现确诊者，城南市于15日对参加过8日礼拜的90多名教徒和全体135名教徒进行了检查。
With the emergence of a confirmed person, the city on the 15th to participate in the 8-day worship of more than 90 believers and all 135 religious inspection.
六、伊朗已完成1000万人排查图8目前伊朗国家动员计划已经完成1000万人的疫情排查工作。
Iran Has Completed 10 Million Checklist Chart 8 The Iranian National Mobilization Plan has completed 10 million people's epidemic mapping.
其中21万人出现头痛、发热等症状，在这21万人中，3万人由于症状严重被送往医疗中心，其中1200人被转至医院，900人住院治疗。
Of these, 210,000 had headaches, fever and other symptoms, of which 30,000 were sent to medical centres because of severe symptoms, 1,200 of whom were transferred to hospitals and 900 were hospitalized.
【特别说明：以上统计，2月28日前为世卫组织官方统计数据，数据截止时间为北京时间每日17时；从2月28日开始，数据由《财经》根据公开资料统计，截止时间为北京时间每日9时】七、全球疫情数字速览：1、【7,000亿美元量化宽松】美联储表示：“新冠肺炎的爆发已经损害了包括美国在内的许多国家的社区并破坏了经济活动。
According to the statistics, the deadline for data is 17: 00 daily Beijing time before Feb. 28. Starting from Feb. 28, data by Caijing is 9: 00pm daily according to open data. The global outbreak of pneumonia has damaged communities and disrupted economic activity in many countries, including the US, the Federal Reserve said
”美联储将利率降至接近零，并启动一项规模达7,000亿美元的大规模量化宽松计划，以保护美国经济免受新冠肺炎的冲击。
The Fed cut interest rates to near zero and launched a massive $700 billion program of quantitative easing to protect the US economy from the new crown pneumonia.
面对高度动荡的金融市场，美联储还将银行贴现窗口的紧急贷款利率下调了125个基点至0.25％，并将贷款期限延长至90天。
The Fed also cut the emergency lending rate at its discount window by 125 basis points to 0.25 per cent in the face of highly volatile financial markets and extended its lending to 90 days.
2、【伦敦-北京机票价35000元】海外疫情不断恶化，飞往中国的航班减少，随之而来的是机票价格暴涨。
LONDON - BEIJING (Reuters) - An international epidemic is worsening, with fewer flights to China, followed by soaring ticket prices.
以3月16日为例，在线购票平台显示，有5趟从伦敦飞往北京的航班机票在售，全部为中转。
On March 16, for example, the online ticketing platform showed that there were five flights from London to Beijing on sale, all in transit.
票价从人民币15,000元至35,000元不等，而且全部是经济舱。
The fares range from 15,000 yuan to 35,000 yuan, all in economy class.
3月16日从法国巴黎起飞至北京的航班有六趟在售，票价最低近1.5万，最高达到47,410元。
Six flights from Paris to Beijing are on sale on March 16, offering fares ranging from a low of nearly 15,000 to a high of 47,410 yuan.
而2019年同期票价最低仅为1,977元。
The lowest ticket price for the same period in 2019 was $1,977.
小结：中国现有确诊病例已降至1万以下。
Summary: The number of confirmed cases in China has dropped to below 10, 000.
国内已采取最严密的入境防疫检测措施，但海外疫情日益严重，回国航班一票难求。
China has adopted the most stringent anti-epidemic measures, but the overseas epidemic is increasingly serious, a return flight ticket is difficult to obtain.
美国继续在快车道上狂奔，但基本防疫措施已经得到重视和加强。
The United States continues to gallop in the fast lane, but basic vaccination measures have been emphasized and strengthened.
